::DeathStorm::

DeathStorm growls as he stumbles backwards from a shot. He hated dealing with 
maximals.

"This is getting nowhere. I'll go find your leader on my own." He says, 
ducking under a shot.

He activates his jetpack and flies off. "Computer," He says, contacting his 
ship's comp, "Start an energy scan for any maximals on this planet."

"Acknowledged. Scan underway."

"Excelent..." DeathStorm mutters and keeps flying.
